{"tid":2083507,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特朗普否認獲知情報俄國獎勵塔利班武裝殺害阿富汗美軍","createTime":"2020-06-28T20:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T20:11:00.000Z","uid":360777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e578925bd7afe02957c378ed919e88a6e00bf0f4","tid":2083507,"uid":360777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T20:05:16.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普否認傳媒報道指稱他獲知情報，俄羅斯向阿富汗塔利班武裝給予獎勵，殺害派駐當地美軍。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》報道，美國情報人員去年獲得這項情報，當時特朗普政府正與塔利班商討阿富汗停火。報道指出，特朗普再次淡化對俄羅斯的指控。外界形容，若果報道屬實，顯示特朗普並沒有捍衛駐阿富汗美軍，對國家安全構成嚴重挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在社交網絡強烈否認，重申沒有人向他匯報，或向副總統彭斯及白宮幕僚長等提及有關俄羅斯襲擊駐阿富汗美軍的情報。他再次指責《紐約時報》發放不明消息來源的假新聞，又表示阿富汗美軍並不是經常受襲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534590-20200629.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534590-20200629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=wLbnxcWodPR608ZqId7G8UXpujcHphTkFDN4g7DGnHE%3D&h=a6d14be3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534590-20200629.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d0a774fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534590-20200629.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4be2d22fe3e88550c1c16bf8a9dcb801ebbd3b11","tid":2083507,"uid":360777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T20:08:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">他再次指責《紐約時報》發放不明消息來源的假新聞</span></strong>"},{"pid":"fc4a30338e4216608a9c63d657e7cfb9c8bb2aad","tid":2083507,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T20:10:33.000Z","msg":"佢敢咁實牙實齒否認應該真係fake<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a9aec89d5050150329617404ab4e71a6bc671a","tid":2083507,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc4a30338e4216608a9c63d657e7cfb9c8bb2aad","tid":2083507,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-